select.id: get高額合算申請書データ

mapper.select:
SELECT row_number() over(partition by "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" order by "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."rirekiNo" ASC) as rowNum,
FROM rgdb."DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho" WHERE
"DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shinseiJokyoKubun" = '1' AND ("DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseisho_SofuYM" IS NULL OR "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseisho_SofuYM" = '' OR "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."saiSofuFlag" = '1') AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."isDeleted" = false
"DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shinseiJokyoKubun" = '1' AND ("DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseisho_SofuYM" IS NULL OR "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseisho_SofuYM" = '' OR "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseisho_SofuYM" = #{処理年月} OR "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."saiSofuFlag" = '1') AND "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."isDeleted" = false
ORDER BY "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" ASC, "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."rirekiNo" ASC, "DbT3068KogakuGassanShinseisho"."hihokenshaNo" ASC

mapper.select:
SELECT 旧市町村."kyuShichosonMeisho" AS shichosonMeisho,
FROM ( SELECt "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho".* FROM "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho" WHERE ("DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shoKisaiHokenshaName" = '' OR "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shoKisaiHokenshaName" IS NULL) AND "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho"."sofuJogaiFlag" = false ) AS DbWT3711 INNER JOIN (SELECT temp_旧市町村.* FROM ( SELECT row_number() over (partition by "DbT7056GappeiShichoson"."kyuHokenshaNo" order by "DbT7056GappeiShichoson"."gappeiYMD" DESC) AS rowNum, "DbT7056GappeiShichoson".* FROM rgdb."DbT7056GappeiShichoson" ) AS temp_旧市町村 WHERE temp_旧市町村.rowNum = 1 ) AS 旧市町村 ON DbWT3711."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = 旧市町村."kyuHokenshaNo"

SELECT 構成市町村."shichosonMeisho" AS shichosonMeisho,
FROM ( SELECt "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho".* FROM "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho" WHERE ("DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shoKisaiHokenshaName" = '' OR "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho"."shoKisaiHokenshaName" IS NULL) AND "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho"."sofuJogaiFlag" = false ) AS DbWT3711 INNER JOIN (SELECT temp.* FROM( SELECT row_number() over (partition by "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster"."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" order by "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster"."kanyuYMD" DESC) AS rowNum, "DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster".* FROM rgdb."DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster" ) AS temp WHERE temp.rowNum = 1 ) AS 構成市町村 ON DbWT3711."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = 構成市町村."shoKisaiHokenshaNo"

select.id: get保険者番号の取得データ

mapper.select: SELECT dbwt3711."hokenshaNo" AS dbwt3711_hokenshaNo, COUNT(DISTINCT(dbwt3711."shikyuShinseishoSeiriNo" || dbwt3711."rirekiNo")) AS dbwt3711_count, COUNT(DISTINCT(dbwt3711."hihokenshaNo" || dbwt3711."taishoNendo" || dbwt3711."seiriNo" || dbwt3711."rirekiNo")) AS hihokenshaNo_count FROM "DbWT3711KogakuGassanShinseisho" AS dbwt3711 WHERE dbwt3711."sofuJogaiFlag" = false GROUP BY dbwt3711."hokenshaNo"
